usage: git clonex [<options>] [<clone-arguments>]

Clone repository

options:
    -h|--help               display help
    -C <work-dir>           same as git '-C' option
    -j<jobs-count>          same as 'git clone' '-j' option (default depends on system)
    -r|--recursive          clone submodules recursively
    
example:
    git clonex -r           clone submodules recursively
